    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>在V1.10版本中，已修复前面发现的所有BUG。社区玩家不同角色通关。敬请放心。<br>另外V1.10加入了英雄副本，新的武学和法术，增加了游戏后期的挑战性和可玩性。</u></h2></strong><br><br>QQ群: 781101235<br><strong><u>开发者强烈建议加入QQ群，查看新手攻略（因为游戏系统较复杂，内容较多），讨论游戏经验。</u></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >        <strong>Roguelike还是rpg？</strong></h2>每次渡劫失败后就是轮回，也就是一次Roguelike的“复活” <br><br>一个特异的Roguelike<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/1a4daf50e27b53e6a073fc6d4b3a8537.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/2750b6202bf7856e7cc037ffcb55fb21.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\t<strong>单机还是网络游戏？</strong></h2>\t6种循环、无限任务<br><br>\t5大副本 再分3种难度 15种挑战<br>\t18场 《西游记》剧情战斗<br>\t20+ 草药材料<br>\t100+ 基础装备  <br>\t5种品质+20余种BUFF 衍生出无法计数的装备<br>\t一个丰富的单机游戏，延长你的游戏体验<br>\t<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/f4a489656d8f03ff78e99fea08d59020.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/02b62475a4b1630317f3d1d7f5fa2b49.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/c79bf0ca718a1537105af46cd5e56023.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/e86c4e583616b3e3befcfb5eecff3c02.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\t<strong>主角还是npc？</strong></h2>\t他们也会做任务，进副本，炼装备…\t<br><br>甚至会主动邀请你探索副本<br>一个个自主的NPC<br>\t<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/6ed027b1b2c9f72779f7fae5a1e85440.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/b8f3a1b862801dbee08024a05a7d1404.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/5a6705bb7113100f28e3cfb95d21e97c.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\t<strong>回合还是战略？</strong></h2>\t不同技能搭配获得不同的BUFF：流血、破甲、治愈、连战… <br><br>80+ 法术&amp;武学<br>100+ 技能搭配<br>无法计数的 技能学习配置<br>\t<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/cecfb2a5c0c40b2ff724cfa5d8891b15.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/b63b6831c8b5326220126ae9c5ba70d6.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/907240/extras/4b541d18eea35e617dacabf48697ddf2.avif?t=1537492692\" width=128 height=128 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\t<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\t<strong>一个系统丰富的独立游戏，或许玩得越久，越能体会到它的精彩之处。</strong></h2></h2>",
